OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FFor ITV Tonight, Daniel Hewitt meets
OL,7,Fthose at the heart of a funding crisis
OL,8,Fthat has hit hospices across the
OL,9,Fcountry
OL,11,FMy mum Diane was 51 when she was
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer.
OL,14,FShe endured countless rounds of
OL,15,Fgruelling chemotherapy, and for five
OL,16,Fyears managed to live a largely full
OL,17,Fand active life alongside her
OL,18,Ftreatment, free of debilitating pain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/28
