OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FAt the beginning of 2014 her condition
OL,7,Fdeteriorated quickly. The final few
OL,8,Fdays of my mum's life were beyond
OL,9,Ftough. Her bravery knew no bounds, but
OL,10,Fbravery is not enough in the face of
OL,11,Fcancer.
OL,13,FShe was dying, and for a short period
OL,14,Fof time she was dying in pain.
OL,16,FThat is when we were referred to our
OL,17,Flocal hospice. Hospices cannot save
OL,18,Fyou, but they save you from the worst
OL,19,Fof what dying can bring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/28
