OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FThey saved my mum from dying in pain,
OL,7,Fand they saved her from dying in a
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,FThere are not enough words in the
OL,11,Fworld to describe the unending
OL,12,Fgratitude we have for the palliative
OL,13,Fcare nurse who came to our house from
OL,14,FSt Giles Hospice in Staffordshire, and
OL,15,Fmade my mum comfortable.
OL,17,FIt meant she could stay in her own
OL,18,Fhome, in her own bed, surrounded by
OL,19,Ffamily.
