OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FData given exclusively to the Tonight
OL,7,Fprogramme by Hospice UK reveals 70% of
OL,8,Fhospices are in financial deficit this
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,F"We estimate that the hospice sector
OL,12,Fas a whole could be facing spending a
OL,13,Fhundred million pounds more than it
OL,14,Fgets in income," Toby Porter, Chief
OL,15,FExecutive of Hopsice UK, told us.
OL,17,F"That is not a sustainable. The sector
OL,18,Fwill just simply start to shrivel."
