OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FThe financial pressures keep coming.
OL,7,FWhen the government announces pay
OL,8,Frises for NHS staff, as it did
OL,9,Frecently, most hospices agree to meet
OL,10,Fthe increase in order to retain nurses
OL,11,Fand doctors, but they don't get any
OL,12,Fgovernment funding to pay for it.
OL,14,FThe money has to come from through
OL,15,Fmore fundraising.
OL,17,FOn top of that, the recent national
OL,18,Finsurance increase in the Budget will
OL,19,Falso hit hospices, who are not exempt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/28
