OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FWe understand discussions are taking
OL,7,Fplace between the sector and
OL,8,Fgovernment ministers.
OL,10,FI have been told the sector has asked
OL,11,Fthe Department of Health for an
OL,12,Fimmediate cash injection of #110m to
OL,13,Favoid cuts to services and jobs before
OL,14,FChristmas.
OL,16,FFor our special Tonight programme, I
OL,17,Fwent been back to St Giles Hospice in
OL,18,FStaffordshire. It is more than a
OL,19,Fdecade since they helped my mum, but
OL,20,Fthings have changed.
