OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FJust 18% of St Giles' funding comes
OL,7,Ffrom the government.
OL,9,FIt means they need to raise more than
OL,10,F#8 million from the local community
OL,11,Fevery year just to stay open, but not
OL,12,Fenough money is coming in.
OL,14,FThe hospice has had to cut 22 jobs
OL,15,Fthis month, and reduce the services it
OL,16,Fprovides. Standing in an empty
OL,17,Finpatient room, St Giles CEO Elinor
OL,18,FEustace tells me it is "madness".
