OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,F"We've got 23 beds here on our
OL,7,Finpatient unit," she said. "We can
OL,8,Fonly afford to run 15, so a room like
OL,9,Fthis is going to be empty because we
OL,10,Fare not able to staff this inpatient
OL,11,Funit.
OL,13,F"It is heartbreaking and it's absolute
OL,14,Fmadness. If we have 23 beds, we can
OL,15,Frelieve more pressure from an already
OL,16,Fstruggling (NHS) system but we
OL,17,Fliterally can't afford to do it."
