OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FHospices are charitable organisations
OL,7,Fbut they play a crucial role in the
OL,8,Fhealthcare system, taking patients out
OL,9,Fof NHS hospitals and away from NHS
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FNatalie Morris has already noticed a
OL,13,Fdifference in the care hospices are
OL,14,Fproviding.
OL,16,FIn 2019, her dad Tony was diagnosed
OL,17,Fwith kidney cancer. He was a TV
OL,18,Fpresenter at the time, a legend of
OL,19,Fregional news at ITV Granada Reports
OL,20,Fin the northwest of England.
