OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FAs his condition deteriorated, he
OL,7,Freceived end-of-life care at Bury
OL,8,FHospice in Lancashire, and Natalie was
OL,9,Fblown away by the treatment.
OL,11,F"I was shocked. I couldn't believe
OL,12,Fthat these places existed," she told
OL,13,Fme.
OL,15,F"My dad had this huge room all to
OL,16,Fhimself, windows that looked out onto
OL,17,Fthis beautiful garden. It felt like we
OL,18,Fwere in our own little bubble. We
OL,19,Fcould be together.
