OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,F"I just think (the staff) are like
OL,7,Fangels on earth, which sounds so over
OL,8,Fthe top, but that's genuinely how it
OL,9,Ffelt in that moment because I'd never
OL,10,Fexperienced such compassion, such
OL,11,Fcare."
OL,13,FTony died peacefully at the hospice in
OL,14,FAugust 2020. Three years later,
OL,15,FNatalie learned her mum Kim was
OL,16,Fseriously unwell.
