OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FDiagnosed with pancreatic cancer, Kim
OL,7,Fknew that she was dying. After seeing
OL,8,Fwhat Tony had been through, she began
OL,9,Fto plan her own hospice care, albeit
OL,10,Fat a different one near where she
OL,11,Flived.
OL,13,FNatalie said: "She was really
OL,14,Fproactive. She went to visit hospices,
OL,15,Fshe made a plan with her GP, and she
OL,16,Fwas very clear that was the path she
OL,17,Fwanted to go down.
