OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,F"The staff were trying their hardest,
OL,7,Fit felt like the resources had been
OL,8,Fpretty brutally stripped," she said.
OL,10,F"For her to be in such a vulnerable
OL,11,Fstate, to be on a shared ward with
OL,12,Fother people, all we could do was pull
OL,13,Fa thin curtain around her bed.
OL,15,F"We didn't get that privacy that we
OL,16,Fwere hoping for, we didn't get that
OL,17,Fspace.
