OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,F"It was heartbreaking to see her in a
OL,7,Fposition where she'd been so
OL,8,Fmeticulous, so careful, so proactive,
OL,9,Fso brave, to then not have the
OL,10,Fexperience that she'd so carefully
OL,11,Fplanned for and hoped for.
OL,13,F"This is a crucial time. You don't get
OL,14,Fa second chance at this. When someone
OL,15,Fis in the last days of their life, you
OL,16,Fdon't get a do over."
OL,18,FKim passed away in September.
