OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FAnother problem with relying so
OL,7,Fheavily on your local community for
OL,8,Fdonations is the glaring wealth
OL,9,Finequality between different parts of
OL,10,Fthe country, with some areas able to
OL,11,Foffer more than others.
OL,13,FSome regions also receive more help
OL,14,Ffrom the government than others, and
OL,15,Fother areas have no hospice service at
OL,16,Fall.
OL,18,FKate, who has terminal breast cancer,
