OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FOn top of the huge financial
OL,7,Fpressures, hospices could be about to
OL,8,Fgrapple with an enormous challenge.
OL,10,FA new bill on assisted dying is set to
OL,11,Fbe debated in Parliament on Friday, a
OL,12,Fcontroversial new law which would
OL,13,Fallow people with a terminal illness
OL,14,Fto end their own life.
OL,16,FSome in the sector believe palliative
OL,17,Fcare needs to be improved first,
OL,18,Fbefore such a momentous decision is
OL,19,Fmade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/28
