OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,F"We carried out a survey in September
OL,7,Fof this year," said Professor
OL,8,FKatherine Sleeman, an expert in
OL,9,Fpalliative medicine at Kings College
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,F"We found that 83% of people who
OL,13,Fsupport assisted dying legalisation
OL,14,Fcite poor palliative care as a reason
OL,15,Ffor their support.
